articles.imgAlt: 10 Week Mass Building Program For Hardgainers
articles.title: 10 Week Mass Building Program
articles.shortSummary:
This workout is designed to increase your
                        muscle mass as much as possible in 10
                        weeks. Works each muscle group hard once
                        per week using mostly heavy compound
                        exercises.

articles.imgAlt: Muscle & Strength’s 12 Week Women’s Workout Program
articles.title:
Muscle & Strength’s 12 Week
                          Women’s Workout Program
articles.shortSummary:
This 12 week women's specific training
                        program is perfect for any healthy woman
                        who is looking to transform her body
                        through a good weight lifting program.

articles.imgAlt: 12 Week Fat Destroyer: Complete Fat Loss Workout & Diet Program
articles.title:
12 Week Fat Destroyer: Complete Fat
                          Loss Workout & Diet Program
articles.shortSummary:
This is a complete 12 week program to
                        help you get ripped. Feature includes
                        detailed diet plan and cardio schedule,
                        along with a 4 day upper/lower muscle
                        building split.

articles.title:
Power Hypertrophy Upper Lower
                          (P.H.U.L.) Workout
articles.shortSummary:
Build both size and strength in this 4
                        day split based around basic compound
                        movements. Get the best of both worlds
                        with bodybuilding and powerlifting.

articles.imgAlt: Muscle & Strength's 30 Day Workout Plan For Women
articles.title:
Muscle & Strength's 30 Day Workout
                          Plan For Women
articles.shortSummary:
Looking for the best place to start
                        working towards a leaner, solid, and
                        stronger body? This thorough workout
                        routine is specifically designed to get
                        you there!

articles.imgAlt: Dumbbell Only Home Or Gym Full Body Workout
articles.title:
Dumbbell Only Home Or Gym Full Body
                          Workout
articles.shortSummary:
Short on equipment? No worries! This
                        dumbbell only workout can be used at home
                        or in the gym for building muscle mass.
                        You can also use this as a muscle shock
                        workout to mix things up.

articles.imgAlt: Shirtless muscular man doing a kettlebell workout in the gym.
articles.title:
45-Minute Kettlebell and Bodyweight
                          Workout for Fat Loss
articles.shortSummary:
This simple, yet effective full body
                        workout maximizes fat loss and overall
                        fitness performance. With very minimal
                        equipment you can burn calories and start
                        moving better.

articles.imgAlt: Strong brunette woman doing dumbbell shoulder presses in the gym.
articles.title:
6-Week Women’s Full Body Strength and
                          Conditioning Workout
articles.shortSummary:
This circuit-style workout will help you
                        torch calories and feel stronger, in a
                        short amount of time. Try this 3-day full
                        body workout for efficient lean muscle
                        gains!

articles.imgAlt: Shirtless male doing abdominal plank in his living room at home
articles.title:
15-Minute Core Conditioning Workout
                          You Can Do Anywhere
articles.shortSummary:
Train your abs effectively and
                        efficiently! This versatile workout can
                        be done with just your bodyweight and
                        should be incorporated into your training
                        plan 2-3 times per week.

articles.imgAlt: Front shot of a lean shirtless african american man doing barbell shoulder press
articles.title:
8-Week Shoulder Workout to Build
                          Cannonball Delts
articles.shortSummary:
Are you ready to step up your shoulder
                        training? This intermediate program can
                        be completed once every 5-7 days for 8
                        weeks to help your delts reach their true
                        potential.

articles.imgAlt: Cropped image of dark skinned male athlete touching knee, feeling sore muscles after injury in gym.
articles.title: 8-Week Knee-Friendly Quad Workout
articles.shortSummary:
This program can help you build bigger
                        legs without taking a big toll on the
                        knees. Incorporate this workout into your
                        existing training plan once a week for
                        massive gains.

articles.imgAlt: Shirtless brunette man doing feet elevated push up's at home
articles.title:
3 Dumbbell and Bodyweight Chest
                          Workouts (No Bench Needed!)
articles.shortSummary:
No bench? No problem. You can still get a
                        solid pec pump using just your bodyweight
                        and dumbbells. Try one of these workouts
                        on your next chest day.
